    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This power lets you distract a beast. Choose a beast that you can see within range. If the beast's Intelligence is 4 or higher, the power fails. Otherwise, the beast must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or be charmed by you for the power's duration. If you or one of your companions harms the target, the power ends.</p>\n<p><strong><em>Force Potency.</em></strong> When you cast this power using a force slot of 2nd level or higher, you can affect one additional beast for each slot level above 1st.</p>",
